    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable example of the A80 platform, featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE inline-six equipped with its original sequential twin-turbocharger setup. This specimen retains its factory-correct Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and Torsen limited-slip differential. The engine bay is surgically clean, showing zero signs of oil weeping or vacuum leaks, while the double-wishbone suspension remains tight and responsive. Every VIN tag is present, confirming an accident-free history and original body panels. This is a collector-grade vehicle with optimal compression across all cylinders and a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation.",
